How to access the nginx webpage?
 -> Location: cd /usr/share/nginx/html/
 -> Create page: sudo vi index.html

How to the nginx configuration?
 -> Location: cd /usr/share/nginx/html/
 -> Access: vim /etc/nginx/nginx.conf


How to troubleshoot the server?
 -> Check Status       : systemctl status <server-name<
 -> Start service      : systemctl start <server-name>
 -> Stop service       : systemctl stop <service-name>
 -> Enable Service     : systemctl enable <service-name>
 -> Check Port status  : netstat -lntp

How to check the log of operations?
 -> Check Error Log    : vim /var/log/messages

How to check the script of files in raghu project ?
 -> Check location     : type disable-auto-shutdown
 -> Cat Location       : cat <location>







